<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.192039>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12 – 16. Homoneura (Homoneura) apicomata sp. nov. Male. 12. protandrium and epandrium, lateral view; 13. protandrium, anterior view; 14. epandrial complex, posterior view; 15. aedeagal complex, ventral view; 16. aedeagal complex, lateral view. Scale 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/192039/files/figure.png" ;
